    "summary_zh": "加尔文的巨著，系统神学的里程碑。全书分四卷：认识创造主上帝、认识救赎主上帝、领受基督恩典的方式（圣灵的工作）、以及上帝设立的外在方式（教会与圣礼）。这部著作奠定了改革宗神学的基础，影响深远，至今仍是神学研究的必读经典。",
    "summary_en": "Calvin's magnum opus and milestone of systematic theology. Four books cover: knowledge of God the Creator, knowledge of God the Redeemer, the means of receiving Christ's grace (the Spirit's work), and the external means God uses (Church and sacraments). This work laid the foundation of Reformed theology and remains an essential classic for theological study.",
