      {
        "number": 1,
        "title_zh": "第一卷第1章：认识上帝与认识自己",
        "title_en": "Book 1 Ch.1: The Knowledge of God and of Ourselves Mutually Connected",
        "summary_zh": "全书的开篇名句：'我们全部的智慧，凡值得称为真正的、可靠的智慧的，可以说包含两个部分：对上帝的认识和对自己的认识。'二者密不可分。",
        "summary_en": "The famous opening: 'Nearly all the wisdom we possess, that is to say, true and sound wisdom, consists of two parts: the knowledge of God and of ourselves.' The two are inseparable.",
        "key_quotes": [
