        "summary_zh": "加尔文系统阐述三位一体教义：上帝的本质是一，位格是三（圣父、圣子、圣灵）。每个位格完全拥有神性，但三者有别。加尔文回应了历史上的各种异端。",
        "summary_en": "Calvin systematically expounds the Trinity: God is one in essence, three in persons (Father, Son, Holy Spirit). Each person fully possesses divinity, yet the three are distinct. Calvin refutes historical heresies.",
        "key_quotes": [
          "The Father is wholly in the Son, the Son wholly in the Father, even as he himself declares: 'I am in the Father, and the Father in me.' 父全在子里面，子全在父里面，正如他自己宣告的：'我在父里面，父在我里面。'"
