        "summary_zh": "上帝不只是创造了世界然后撒手不管。他时刻掌管万有，一切事情都在他的旨意和掌控之下。这不是宿命论，而是信靠的基础——没有任何事超出上帝的主权。",
        "summary_en": "God did not create the world and then step back. He continually governs all things under His will. This is not fatalism but the foundation of trust—nothing is beyond God's sovereignty.",
        "key_quotes": [
          "For he is deemed omnipotent, not because he can indeed act, yet sometimes ceases and sits in idleness... but because, governing heaven and earth by his providence, he so regulates all things that nothing takes place without his deliberation. 他被视为全能的，不是因为他有能力行动却有时停止、闲坐不动……而是因为他以护理统管天地，万事的发生都不偏离他的旨意。"
