        "summary_en": "Adam's fall affected not only himself but all humanity. Original sin is an inherited corruption—from soul to body, the whole person is tainted by sin.",
        "key_quotes": [
          "Original sin is the hereditary corruption and depravity of our nature, extending to every part of the soul. 原罪是我们本性中遗传的败坏和堕落，延伸到灵魂的每个部分。"
