          "Man will be said to have this sort of free decision, not because he has a free choice of good and evil, but because he acts wickedly by will, not by compulsion. 人可以被说成有某种自由抉择，不是因为他可以自由选择善或恶，而是因为他作恶是出于意愿，而非出于被迫。"
