        "summary_zh": "加尔文系统阐述预定论：上帝在创世以前就拣选了一些人得救。这不是基于上帝预见人的信心，而是完全出于上帝自主的恩典。预定论的目的是让人将一切荣耀归于上帝。",
        "summary_en": "Calvin systematically expounds predestination: before creation, God chose some for salvation. This is not based on foreseen faith but entirely on God's sovereign grace. Predestination's purpose is to ascribe all glory to God.",
        "key_quotes": [
          "We call predestination God's eternal decree, by which he determined with himself what he willed to become of each man. For all are not created in equal condition; rather, eternal life is foreordained for some, eternal damnation for others. 我们所称的预定，是上帝永恒的旨意——他在自己里面决定了每个人的命运。因为所有人不是被造于同等条件之下；倒是永生为某些人预定，永死为另一些人预定。"
