        "summary_en": "Plantinga formulates the problem of evil as formal logical argument. Critics claim God's omnibenevolence and omnipotence are logically incompatible with evil's existence. If this incompatibility holds, theism is logically impossible.",
        "key_quotes": [
          "逻辑的恶的问题声称发现了有神论信念集合中的逻辑矛盾。/ The logical problem of evil claims to discover logical contradiction in the theistic belief set.",
