        "summary_en": "Lewis's prophetic warning: when humanity attempts to 'conquer' nature through technology and reason, it ultimately leads to the abolition of human nature itself. 'Conditioners' (the few who possess human-reshaping technology) will remake humanity according to their subjective values rather than objective moral law, leading to the end of authentic humanity.",
        "key_quotes": [
