        "summary_en": "Argues for the certainty of true believers' final salvation. Saints' perseverance doesn't depend on human willpower but on God's faithfulness and Christ's intercession. The authors address \"losing salvation\" concerns, explaining that genuinely regenerated persons may fall but won't completely abandon faith because God preserves them to the end.",
        "key_quotes": [
